entries.title_d: The drop ship pilot's description of the enemy flight leader has peeked Insurgent's interest. You are to patrol the region and look for any sign of the enemy. Be on the look out for any enemy officers that might have more information on the enemy flight leader.
entries.title: Dathomir System: Patrol the Dathomir System
entries.split_quest_alert: Scans indicate a ship bearing the markings of an officer located. Disable and inspect that ship for their order data.
entries.quest_patrol_d: When you reach a navigation waypoint you will receive a new one to the next location. Follow the patrol waypoints until you come to the end of your patrol.
entries.quest_location_d: Remain in the Dathomir system and follow the patrol navigation waypoints. As you reach one navigation waypoint, you will get a new waypoint to the next location on the patrol route.
